General.Name: Combined Motor Holdings Limited
General.Description: Combined Motor Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the motor retail and car hire businesses in South Africa. It offers new and used vehicles, parts, and related services; and life, disability, dread disease, retrenchment, and vehicle and component warranty insurance products, as well as vehicle financing solutions. The company operates a fleet of approximately 7,500 vehicles through First Car Rental. In addition, it is involved in the distribution and franchising business; digital marketing, and workshop equipment; and supply and installation of workshop lifting, lubrication and diagnostic equipment, and the supply of waterless car wash systems. Combined Motor Holdings Limited was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Umhlanga, South Africa.
